{"tid":2194440,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"Wetland seasons park 第三期應該又過萬飛","createTime":"2020-09-08T13:23:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-09T16:23:55.000Z","uid":92439,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"76454e50e36fa85638aac2404ebd658ea19ecef6","tid":2194440,"uid":92439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T13:23:55.000Z","msg":"【新盤價單】Wetland Seasons Park第3期1房折實413.3萬起<br />\n16:09 2020/09/08<br />\n<br />\n疫情回穩，多個全新盤部署出擊，「月月有樓賣」的新地旗下天水圍濕地公園路新盤Wetland Seasons Park第3期首張價單涉及65伙，包括1房至3房單位，發展商提供最高18%折扣，Wetland Seasons Park第3期1房折實價由413.3萬起元。<br />\n<br />\n現場所見Wetland Seasons Park第3期第9座1樓B2室，面積316平方呎1房，價單定價504.03萬元，即供最高折扣18%，折實售價413.3萬元，折實呎價13,079元。<br />\n<br />\n資料顯示，Wetland Seasons Park第1期去年12月公布首張價單時，當時折實最平480.42萬、折實呎價最平9,988元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2747211/%E3%80%90%E6%96%B0%E7%9B%A4%E5%83%B9%E5%96%AE%E3%80%91Wetland%20Seasons%20Park%E7%AC%AC3%E6%9C%9F1%E6%88%BF%E6%8A%98%E5%AF%A6413.3%E8%90%AC%E8%B5%B7?mtc=20023\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2747211%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%259B%25A4%25E5%2583%25B9%25E5%2596%25AE%25E3%2580%2591Wetland%2520Seasons%2520Park%25E7%25AC%25AC3%25E6%259C%259F1%25E6%2588%25BF%25E6%258A%2598%25E5%25AF%25A6413.3%25E8%2590%25AC%25E8%25B5%25B7%3Fmtc%3D20023&d=pZTDRaRh7CFw%2FURiZY0DNcdEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=268cf941\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2747211/%E3%80%90%E6%96%B0%E7%9B%A4%E5%83%B9%E5%96%AE%E3%80%91Wetland%20Seasons%20Park%E7%AC%AC3%E6%9C%9F1%E6%88%BF%E6%8A%98%E5%AF%A6413.3%E8%90%AC%E8%B5%B7?mtc=20023</a><br />\n<br />\n入飛 pm我 tg: chriswong963"},{"pid":"c7bb91d62e0c1c4f4aee165ce32732ab3a1e7b73","tid":2194440,"uid":43033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76454e50e36fa85638aac2404ebd658ea19ecef6","tid":2194440,"uid":92439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T13:23:55.000Z","msg":"【新盤價單】Wetland Seasons Park第3期1房折實413.3萬